    • Method Detail

      • convertMethodToFunction

        TypeI convertMethodToFunction()
        Creates a new function type B based on the original function type A. Takes the receiver type (this type) of A and makes it the first argument of B; B has no receiver type. Used by the DevirtualizePrototypeMethods pass.
